data.title: About: Wayland, Massachusetts
data.meta_description: Wayland is a town in Middlesex County, Massachusetts, United States. The town was founded in 1638, and incorporated in 1780 and was originally part of neighboring Sudbury (incorporated 1639). As of the 2020 United States Census, the population was 13,943. In 2021, Niche.com ranked Wayland as #1 on their list of "Best Places to Raise a Family in Massachusetts", #8 on their list of "Best Places to Raise a Family in America", and #2 on their list of "Best Suburbs to Live in Massachusetts".
data.text:
dbo:abstract

Wayland és una població dels Estats Units a l'estat de Massachusetts. Segons el cens del 2007 tenia una població de 13.017 habitants. (ca)

Wayland ist eine Kleinstadt im Middlesex County des Bundesstaats Massachusetts in den Vereinigten Staaten. Das U.S. Census Bureau hat bei der Volkszählung 2020 eine Einwohnerzahl von 13.943 ermittelt. Wayland ist Teil der Metropolregion Greater Boston. (de)

Wayland es un pueblo ubicado en el condado de Middlesex en el estado estadounidense de Massachusetts. En el Censo de 2010 tenía una población de 12.994 habitantes y una densidad poblacional de 316,63 personas por km².​ (es)

Wayland Ameriketako Estatu Batuetako inkorporatutako herri bat da. Middlesex konderrian kokatuta dago, Massachusetts estatuan. 13.444 biztanle ditu, 15,9 kilometro koadroko azaleran banatuta. (eu)

Wayland est une ville du Comté de Middlesex dans l’État du Massachusetts. Elle a été incorporée en 1780. Sa population était de 13 943 habitants en 2020. (fr)

Wayland è un comune degli Stati Uniti d'America facente parte della contea di Middlesex nello stato del Massachusetts. (it)

Wayland is a town in Middlesex County, Massachusetts, United States. The town was founded in 1638, and incorporated in 1780 and was originally part of neighboring Sudbury (incorporated 1639). As of the 2020 United States Census, the population was 13,943. In 2021, Niche.com ranked Wayland as #1 on their list of "Best Places to Raise a Family in Massachusetts", #8 on their list of "Best Places to Raise a Family in America", and #2 on their list of "Best Suburbs to Live in Massachusetts". (en)

Wayland is een plaats (town) in Middlesex County, Massachusetts, Verenigde Staten. In 2000 had de plaats een inwonertal van 13100 en waren er 4625 huishoudens. (nl)

Wayland – miasto w Stanach Zjednoczonych, w stanie Massachusetts, w hrabstwie Middlesex. (pl)

Wayland är en kommun (town) i Middlesex County i Massachusetts. Kommunen hade 2001 en befolkning på ungefär 13 100 invånare. (sv)

Вейленд (англ. Wayland) — місто (англ. town) в США, в окрузі Міддлсекс штату Массачусетс. Населення — 12 994 особи (2010). (uk)

Wayland é uma vila localizada no condado de Middlesex no estado estadounidense de Massachusetts. No Censo de 2010 tinha uma população de 12.994 habitantes e uma densidade populacional de 316,63 pessoas por km². (pt)
